src.lib.FPGA_PID_Loop_Simple_lib_Wrapper module¶

Created on Wed Oct 22 17:46:08 2014

@author: Jan Gieseler

Wrapper for c-compiled FPGA_PID_Loop_Simple.vi (complied into FPGA_PID_lib.dll) here we wrap the c-functions that can are then accessed by the higher level FPGA_PID_Loop_Simple.py which defines the higher level Python objects that are then used to interact with the NI FPGA
